{"tid":1917911,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞典著名演員麥士·馮·西度（Max von Sydow）逝世，享年90歲","createTime":"2020-03-09T18:37:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T10:53:06.000Z","uid":35221,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8f6b6f3f40ba8f428c51060b4fde6c982e5bb5f9","tid":1917911,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T18:37:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://maddog.myradio.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/max-von-sydow.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaddog.myradio.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2Fmax-von-sydow.jpg&h=083b9db3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n演技派老演員瑞典籍演員麥斯[麥士]&middot;馮&middot;西度（MAX VON SYDOW）今早去世，死因未有公佈，享年90歲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BM2I1ZWU4YjMtYzU0My00YmMzLWFmNTAtZDJhZGYwMmI3YWQ5XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjU0OTQ0OTY@._V1_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.media-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FM%2FMV5BM2I1ZWU4YjMtYzU0My00YmMzLWFmNTAtZDJhZGYwMmI3YWQ5XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjU0OTQ0OTY%40._V1_.jpg&h=955c64ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《第七封印》(The Seventh Seal)<br />\n<br />\n馮&middot;西度是一名瑞典籍演員，同時持法國護照。他曾出演多部電影中的配角。在表演時使用過多種語言，包括英語、西班牙語、意大利語、德語、瑞典語、挪威語、丹麥語、法語、以及西班牙語。 最令觀眾難忘的電影角色，包括在英格瑪&middot;柏格曼導演的電影《第七(封)印》（THE SEVENTH SEAL），從影生涯曾經兩度獲得奧斯卡獎提名。其中，馮‧西度於電影《響在耳邊，近在眼前》（EXTREMELY LOUD AND INCREDIBLY CLOSE）中，「0」台詞挑戰奧斯卡最佳男配角。他在電影中飾演一名不願開口說話的陌生房客，他的豐富和內斂的表情讓所有的情緒盡在不言中，完全展現其演技派實力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/39/10/5a/39105a23ad62dd1dd10f0cef5f4c5fb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F39%2F10%2F5a%2F39105a23ad62dd1dd10f0cef5f4c5fb9.jpg&h=f44dde1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《響在耳邊，近在眼前》(Extremely Loud and Incredibly Close)<br />\n<br />\n另外，馮‧西度最為香港觀眾熟悉是曾香港武打巨星成龍合作出演火拼時速3（RUSH HOUR 3）以及於經典大作《星球大戰：原力覺醒》（STAR WARS 7）的演出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.comicbook.com/2020/03/max-von-sydow-star-wars-1210167-1280x0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.comicbook.com%2F2020%2F03%2Fmax-von-sydow-star-wars-1210167-1280x0.jpeg&h=bb741928&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《星球大戰：原力覺醒》（Star Wars: The Force Awakens）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://maddog.myradio.hk/2020/03/09/newsdesk/international/%E8%91%97%E5%90%8D%E6%BC%94%E5%93%A1%E9%BA%A5%E6%96%AF%C2%B7%E9%A6%AE%C2%B7%E8%A5%BF%E5%BA%A6%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96-%E4%BA%AB%E5%B9%B490%E6%AD%B2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaddog.myradio.hk%2F2020%2F03%2F09%2Fnewsdesk%2Finternational%2F%25E8%2591%2597%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%25BC%2594%25E5%2593%25A1%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E6%2596%25AF%25C2%25B7%25E9%25A6%25AE%25C2%25B7%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E9%2580%259D%25E4%25B8%2596-%25E4%25BA%25AB%25E5%25B9%25B490%25E6%25AD%25B2%2F&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FM45RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=2dd6a2be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://maddog.myradio.hk/2020/03/09/newsdesk/international/%E8%91%97%E5%90%8D%E6%BC%94%E5%93%A1%E9%BA%A5%E6%96%AF%C2%B7%E9%A6%AE%C2%B7%E8%A5%BF%E5%BA%A6%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96-%E4%BA%AB%E5%B9%B490%E6%AD%B2/</a>"},{"pid":"5501a129118aafbbc57b6e97082db40e7b9b87c5","tid":1917911,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T18:40:12.000Z","msg":"who"},{"pid":"7a9f8f0cd3d464b5450c2f619ed0e2914477aeb4","tid":1917911,"uid":35221,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T18:40:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1557/15576725/3642446-merrin.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgamespot1.cbsistatic.com%2Fuploads%2Foriginal%2F1557%2F15576725%2F3642446-merrin.jpg&h=82115ec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《驅魔人》(The Exorcist)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/NINTCHDBPICT000569562232.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2FNINTCHDBPICT000569562232.jpg&h=14810e2b&s={SIZE}\" />